title: Chair Yellen's remarks at 2014 Assets Learning Conference of the Corporation for Enterprise Development
content: - 3 -    stakeholders involved in community development, I believe the Fed can help you in   carrying out your mission, to encourage families to take the small steps that over time can   lead to the accumulation of considerable assets.   Thank you for the chance to be a small part of this conference, and for your   commitment to a cause that I strongly support.
